Paper: hep-th/9311106

Date: 1993-11-18

Title: Axial Monopoles, The Quantization of Electric Charge and a Dynamical

Discreteness of Space-TimeAuthors: S.C.S. Silva, P.C.R.C. Mello and M.C. Nemes

Comments: 9 pages

In the present contribution we show that the introduction of a conservedaxial current in electrodynamics can explain the quantization of electriccharge, preserving parity conservation, and introduces a dynamical discretenessinto space-time.